m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +4 light mace grants its wielder a +5 morale {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Persuasion}Persuasion{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Skills}skill checks{/g} when used to intimidate. m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +5 vicious mithral light mace has 19–20/×2 {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical{/g} range and deals {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}bludgeoning{/g}, slashing and piercing {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: The inscription on this mace reads: "I hate you, {Name}. I hate you so much." Whoever looks at it, sees their own name.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever this +4 light mace deals sneak {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}, it's increased by {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: A word "Surprise!" is crudely burned on the handle.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: Whenever the wielder of this +2 mithral light mace lands the first hit against a new target with it, the enemy has to pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 15) or become stunned for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d3{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.
Whenever this +1 light mace confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g}, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d8{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

Whenever this +3 ghost touch light mace confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g}, the wielder is affected with the effect of a greater invisibility {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} for {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d4{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.

Whenever this +2 light mace confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g} on an enemy, the enemy suffers an additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}3d4{/g} positive {g|Encyclopedia:Energy_Damage}energy damage{/g}; if the enemy is killed the wielder gets +2 {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack rolls{/g} for the next 2 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.

This +5 freezing light mace is emanating an aura that makes enemies in a 10-foot radius suffer a -2 {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack{/g} and {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage rolls{/g} with ranged weapons.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
